<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4760984>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs. 9-14. Kathroperla siskiyou eggs, Split Rock Creek, Jackson Co., Oregon. 9. Entire egg, lateral aspect. 10. Entire egg with intact anchor. 11. Collar end chorionic detail. 12. Collar, apical aspect. 13. Anterior pole. 14. Chorionic detail (micropyle at arrow)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4760984/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4760978>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs. 1-6. Kathroperla perdita eggs. 1-4. Ross Creek, Lincoln Co., Montana. 5-6. Grande Ronde River, Union Co., Oregon. 1. Egg, lateral. 2. Chorionic detail (lt = linear tubercle; m = micropyle). 3. Collar end of egg (a = anchor). 4. Anterior pole (lid) of egg. 5. Collar end of egg (s = stria). 6. Anterior pole of egg." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4760978/files/figure.png" .

